snippet.title: Our World Is Ended. - Character Trailer
snippet.description:
A new masterpiece of narrative visual novel storytelling. 

Meet the Judgement 7 team, outlandish developers working from their Asakusa office. On a summer’s day their AR headset let them catch a glimpse of Tokyo in ruins.

Could it really be the end of the world?

Pre-order Now! 
http://pqube.co.uk/our-world-is-ended/

http://oreowa.jp/

#OurWorldIsEnded
